title: Bloomberg Markets: Wolff on Tech Rebound From Recent Sell Off
itunes:title: Bloomberg Markets: Wolff on Tech Rebound From Recent Sell Off
description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Max Wolff Market Strategist 55 Capital Discussing tech stocks rebounding from last week's sell off saying there are no deals in tech growth but companies from the sector are delivering on big multiples.
